<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_nuvo_diag_probes"><x_nuvo_diag_probes action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Checking for duplicate overrides of Nuvolo Properties</description><name>Duplicate Nuv Properties - Reservations</name><order/><probe_type display_value="Reservation">5913c9091bac1510ae5b21b5ec4bcbc4</probe_type><remediation>Go to Nuvolo Properties list and remove the extra override. </remediation><script><![CDATA[var util = new x_nuvo_diag.DiagnosticUtil();

var x = util.checkDupliateOverrides('Space Reservation');

if (x != false) {
	util.handleOutput('There is a Nuvolo Property ' + x + ', that has two overrides within the Nuvolo Properties table. Each Nuvolo Property should have at maximum one override value', 'Warning',true);
}]]></script><sys_class_name>x_nuvo_diag_probes</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>Michael.Piazza@nuvolo.com</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-07-13 16:15:44</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>c22e99eb1bacdd10ae5b21b5ec4bcba8</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Duplicate Nuv Properties - Reservations</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Diagnostic Tool" source="x_nuvo_diag">3acdaefd1be7fc107798a9b7624bcb74</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Diagnostic Tool">3acdaefd1be7fc107798a9b7624bcb74</sys_scope><sys_update_name>x_nuvo_diag_probes_c22e99eb1bacdd10ae5b21b5ec4bcba8</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Michael.Piazza@nuvolo.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-07-13 16:15:44</sys_updated_on></x_nuvo_diag_probes></record_update>
